      "raw_text": "BOISE, Idaho, Feb. 20. - Judge\nSmith of Caldwell today ordered a\ngrand Jury for next Monday and\nwitnesses were summoned to testi-\nfly against Meyer, Haywood, Petit\nbone and others, charged with the\nmurder of Steunenberg. Attorney\nRichardson announced the federal\ncourt would be invoked to test the\nauthority of a state to abduct the\ncitizens Of Colorado without an op-\nportunity to establish their inno-\ncence."
    }
